#CREATING A RANDOM BAND NAME GENERATOR

#Tasks:
  #1 Create a greeting
  #2 Ask the user for the city that they born in
  #3 Ask the user for the name of an animal
  #4 Combine the name of the city and animal and show them their band name
  #5 Make sure the input cursor shows on a new line

print("Welcome to the Random Band Name Generator!")
print("Please answer the following questions:")
adjective = input("In one word, how do you feel right now?\n")
city = input("What city were you born in?\n")
animal = input("What's your favorite animal?\n" )
print("The name of your band could be "+adjective+" "+city+" "+animal+"s"+"!")
